WEBVTT

00:00.958 --> 00:03.320
Previously on The Passage...
This could alter

00:03.323 --> 00:04.913
the course of Elizabeth's Alzheimer's.

00:04.916 --> 00:06.006
This is for you.

00:06.009 --> 00:07.516
No, this is for you.

00:07.519 --> 00:08.570
She's ten.

00:08.572 --> 00:10.354
She needs fresh air.

00:10.357 --> 00:12.240
Now we have a bird's-eye
view of Project Noah.

00:12.242 --> 00:14.051
Sierra Thompson died earlier today

00:14.054 --> 00:15.409
in a single-car accident.

00:15.412 --> 00:16.712
They killed her.

00:17.703 --> 00:19.114
Why did you change your mind

00:19.116 --> 00:20.348
about the execution?

00:21.785 --> 00:23.986
We've got $36 million
invested per viral.

00:23.988 --> 00:26.286
Guess nobody wants to set
that much cash on fire.

00:26.288 --> 00:27.922
There's a guy on the roof.

00:30.292 --> 00:32.994
Amy, Amy.

00:32.996 --> 00:36.018
The virals aren't gonna break
out. We're gonna let 'em out.

00:36.021 --> 00:36.931
No!

00:36.933 --> 00:38.432
I don't want to die.
Then don't.

00:38.434 --> 00:40.768
Anthony!

00:41.804 --> 00:43.538
Whose blood is that?

00:45.000 --> 00:51.074
